    "content": "<p><strong>Yes — the Philippine Pickleball Federation (PPF) has officially partnered with DUPR (Dynamic Universal Pickleball Rating), giving Filipino players access to the global standard rating system used by top professionals worldwide.</strong> The partnership, announced on June 22, 2026, marks a significant milestone in the professionalization of Philippine pickleball.</p><h3>What is DUPR?</h3><p>DUPR is the world's most accurate pickleball rating system, used by over 1.5 million players globally. Unlike other rating systems that rely on self-assessment or tournament results alone, DUPR uses a sophisticated algorithm that considers every match played, the margin of victory, and the strength of opponents to calculate a player's true skill level.</p><p>Ratings range from 2.0 (beginner) to 8.0 (world-class professional). The system is recognized by the International Pickleball Federation (IPF), the APP Tour, and the PPA Tour.</p><h3>Benefits for Filipino Players</h3><p>With this partnership, every PPF-sanctioned tournament in the Philippines will now contribute to players' DUPR ratings. This means Filipino players can build a verifiable global rating without leaving the country.</p><p>\"Before DUPR, our players had limited ways to demonstrate their skill level internationally,\" says PPF President Ramon Villanueva. \"Now, a player from Cagayan de Oro can earn a DUPR rating that is recognized everywhere from Florida to Frankfurt.\"</p><h3>How to Get Your DUPR Rating</h3><p>Filipino players can get a DUPR rating by: (1) Playing in any PPF-sanctioned tournament, (2) Attending a DUPR rating clinic, or (3) Submitting match results through the DUPR app with a verified opponent. The first option is most common — simply play a tournament and your first six matches establish your initial rating.</p><p>The DUPR app is available for iOS and Android. After creating an account and linking it to your PPF membership, every sanctioned match you play will automatically update your rating.</p><p>For competitive players, this partnership is a game-changer. A strong DUPR rating opens doors to international tournaments, sponsorship opportunities, and even college scholarships abroad.</p>",
